{"tid":688762,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★刊勞工處招聘廣告留假傳真　電話停用玩殘求職者","createTime":"2018-06-03T13:35:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-06T09:43:04.000Z","uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"58806cb90c62924ae26c99f5fce96527b20cacef","tid":688762,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T13:35:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180603/photo/bkn-20180603201304712-0603_00822_001_01b.jpg?20180603204113\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180603%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180603201304712-0603_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20180603204113&h=beeecc69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n打工仔搵工難，近日刊登在勞工處互動就業服務一則空缺啟事，在聯絡方法上將傳真號碼寫成12345678，就算利用啟事上的電話號碼聯絡，只獲得以下回覆，「唔好意思，閣下所打的電話已經停止服務」，玩殘一眾應徵者。<br />\n<br />\n該啟事在本月1日刊登，內容為聘請「助理平水員(墨斗)」一職，其職責為協助平水員開墨線，資歷只須中三程度，要求良好粵語，一般英語，以及讀寫中、英文能力。<br />\n<br />\n薪酬方面可算不俗，只須中三學歷，月薪就約有1.3萬至1.5萬港元，工時則是6天制，由上午8時半至下午5時半。既然薪酬可達1.5萬，那不妨一試應徵，但一看到「申請須知」一欄就令人摸不着頭腦，其傳真號碼竟寫上12345678。<br />\n<br />\n東網記者根據啟事所寫的電話聯絡負責人，但電話傳來的語音指已停止服務。記者亦搜尋招聘職位公司，發現從去年開始已聘請有關職位，但未有留下任何聯絡方式。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180603/bkn-20180603201304712-0603_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180603%2Fbkn-20180603201304712-0603_00822_001.html&d=MjM4JMG%2BNWi3m7oXykWPozA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=ffa47388\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180603/bkn-20180603201304712-0603_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"d86700c5f3a9b83f7e10e1ff660c6fee7ec10e4d","tid":688762,"uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T13:36:07.000Z","msg":"請唔到人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a46dff301af5e1ad788eb67c7e98d5bc97857d3","tid":688762,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T13:36:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b5fbeab2b1cfe0dedd569c9f5b6724b43a276e1","tid":688762,"uid":45772,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d86700c5f3a9b83f7e10e1ff660c6fee7ec10e4d","tid":688762,"uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T13:36:07.000Z","msg":"請唔到人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T13:38:47.000Z","msg":"咁要引入外勞喇"},{"pid":"02c5164eb69920c442e20fed989603b962d8f4ab","tid":688762,"uid":19454,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T13:38:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20170926/large/1506418590_5d74.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170926%2Flarge%2F1506418590_5d74.jpg&h=3c0e772b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2a2016c225579606335fafe4e22fb6ccb2c91d78","tid":688762,"uid":36432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T13:52:10.000Z","msg":"係咪個記者搵工時候發現？"},{"pid":"2460a6cdbf739db63b71f8b92748c11482e914eb","tid":688762,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T08:48:54.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"44863a55e338faf59558166eee6172a288563bef","tid":688762,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T09:06:19.000Z","msg":"話明email"},{"pid":"934012ae3d91eeabcabbc8827c386e9f3ccb26b3","tid":688762,"uid":21917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T09:08:46.000Z","msg":"其實真係仲有人fax ？"},{"pid":"70e77d1954d4b9c6554d21061dbbbde407a1f130","tid":688762,"uid":88250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"934012ae3d91eeabcabbc8827c386e9f3ccb26b3","tid":688762,"uid":21917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T09:08:46.000Z","msg":"其實真係仲有人fax ？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T09:13:46.000Z","msg":"政府部門同艾－基佬"},{"pid":"907a3932c2fcfdbc6c1b16e9c5cdfa24f5cd37ae","tid":688762